    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concedimus <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/1927">Radelchis</persName>, filius
                        dulcis recordationis domni <persName key="#Princeps" ref="#people/115"
                            >Adelchis</persName>, ob salutem gentis nostre et patrię, concedimus in
                            <orgName key="#Churches" ref="#juridical_persons/85"><rs key="#Churches"
                                >ęcclesiam</rs> Sancte Sophie</orgName> que edificata esse videtur
                        infra hanc nostram Beneventanam civitatem <rs
                            key="#Gualdi #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_churches #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >gualdo</rs> quod est [*****************] discurrere solet, id est ab
                        ipso <placeName ref="#places/3461"
                            key="#Gualdi #Fisheries #Fiscal_property #Rights_of_use_on_woods/pastures/waters"
                            >vado carrario</placeName> subtus <orgName key="#Churches"
                            ref="#juridical_persons/3438"><rs key="#Churches">ecclesiam</rs> Sancti
                            Marciani</orgName> usque subtus casa Valerii [*****] integre ipse <rs
                            key="#Marshes/lagoons/tombolos">iscle</rs> ex eo <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >fluvio</rs> pertinentes, ut a nunc et semper homines de ipsa ęcclesia
                        in predicto fluvio <rs key="#Fisheries">piscationem</rs> faciant et ipse
                        iscle omnibus vestris utilitatibus peragendum, in ea videlicet ratione ut
                        amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum supra phatum
                        monasterium eiusque rectores in iam dicto fluvio et iscle habere et
                        possidere valeas et a nullo ex nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus,
                        gastaldis vel quibuscumque agentibus habeas aliquam requisitionem, sed
                        perpetuis temporibus possideas Quod vero preceptus concessionis ex iussione
                        nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName key="#Notary" ref="#people/3468"
                            >Erchemfrid</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventum</placeName> primo anno, mense iulio, quarta
                        decima indictione. Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
